
# Styling & Design Standards

## Color Scheme
- **Primary**: Green theme (#10b981) - Slytherin-inspired
- **Background**: Dark mode as default with light mode support
- **Text**: High contrast ratios for accessibility
- **Accents**: Subtle gradients and hover effects

## Typography
- **Font**: Inter font family for clean, modern look
- **Hierarchy**: Clear heading sizes (text-4xl, text-2xl, text-lg)
- **Weight**: Balanced use of font weights (normal, medium, semibold, bold)
- **Line Height**: Comfortable reading with proper line spacing

## Layout Principles
- **Mobile-first**: Responsive design starting from mobile
- **Grid System**: CSS Grid and Flexbox for layout structure
- **Spacing**: Consistent spacing using Tailwind scale (4, 8, 12, 16, 20, 24, 32)
- **Container**: Max-width containers for content readability

## Component Styling
- **Portfolio Cards**: Consistent card pattern with hover effects
- **Buttons**: Primary and secondary button variants
- **Forms**: Clean input styling with focus states
- **Navigation**: Smooth scroll and active state indicators

## Animations & Interactions
- **Fade-in**: Scroll-triggered animations using Intersection Observer
- **Hover Effects**: Subtle hover states on interactive elements
- **Transitions**: Smooth transitions for state changes
- **Performance**: CSS transforms for better performance

## Design Patterns
```css
/* Portfolio Card Pattern */
.portfolio-card {
  @apply bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300;
}

/* Primary Button Pattern */
.btn-primary {
  @apply px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-300;
}

/* Fade-in Animation */
.fade-in {
  @apply opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-700;
}

.fade-in.visible {
  @apply opacity-100 translate-y-0;
}
```

## Dark/Light Mode
- Use CSS custom properties for theme switching
- Maintain consistent contrast ratios in both modes
- Test all colors in both themes
- Provide smooth theme transitions

- Keep animations subtle and purposeful
- Use `scroll-smooth` for navigation
